OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry day. After a
OL,6,Frather cloudy start - especially in
OL,7,Fthe north - the cloud will break up to
OL,8,Fallow some sunny spells again. Warm in
OL,9,Fthe southeast, cooler around the north
OL,10,Fcoast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will stay dry throughout
OL,13,Fthe evening and overnight. Some spells
OL,14,Fof evening sunshine but gradually
OL,15,Fturning hazier. Some clear spells
OL,16,Fpossible overnight, cloudier in the
OL,17,Fnorth.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,173,160,301,260,100,100
