OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FDry and warm with lengthy
OL,6,Fsunny spells for much of the day, but
OL,7,Fcloud spreads south in the evening
OL,8,Fwith the odd spot of light rain
OL,9,Fpossible in the north.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCloudy
OL,12,Fstarts with some patchy light rain in
OL,13,Fthe north. Warm sunny intervals
OL,14,Fdeveloping in the south through the
OL,15,Fafternoons, staying cloudier and
OL,16,Fcooler in the north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
